00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:32,320
 So just going with the scientists, big science, most likely will be a very, very long way.

382
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:36,380
 And having the private sector also involved may speed it up.

383
00:36:36,380 --> 00:36:42,660
 Now going to another fusion technology that works with fusion, is renewable energy.

