00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:47,120
 Well, the deuterium is in the sun.

387
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:48,960
 Sun is a fusion reactor.

388
00:36:49,620 --> 00:36:51,180
 And in a way, that's the working reactor.

389
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:59,800
 And of course, renewable energy is energy from the sun, which converts itself into hydropower or in direct solar or in the wind power.

