00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:05,380
 And here we have seen tremendous improvements in the last years.

391
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:18,520
 In the figure you see on the upper part of the curves, sorry, the price decline over years, a huge price decline during the last 10 years in solar, wind, and also in batteries,

